  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You can exploit the weaknesses in your opponents' defenses, like a flame seeking fuel to consume.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Int 13; Wis 13; Combat Expertise; Perfect Style; Stunning Fist; Unblinking Flame Feint; base attack bonus +13 or monk level 13th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When using Perfect Style, the save DC of your stunning fist attack increases by 2 against flat-footed targets. When you spend 1 ki point to gain the benefits of Improved Feint for 1 round, you can attempt a feint as part of your movement when charging.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 2 stamina points instead of 1 ki point when using Unblinking Flame Fist.",
